ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The Working Group is a great opportunity to work collaboratively with fellow graduate students and faculty. Yes, I have already recommended others to join the group next year.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Because we're constantly reading things outside of our field/area of expertise, I think it gives me a better sense of the type of projects and scholarly trends in other fields. This is very important since graduate school often does not provide a space for this. I also appreciated how the Working Group actively carves out spaces for public presentations.
